<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/917987-am-i-the-only-one-haunted-by-gauri-nearly">Am I the only one haunted by Gauri nearly committing suicide on the balcony back in Kolkata? I love that scene. And I so much wanted her to jump; I thought she was going to do so. I felt like that would have been appropriate, as bad as that sounds, I know.</a>
</div>
